sting backend interface surface working for Create, Get, Update, Claim, Close, DepAdd, DepRemove, AppendEvent, ExportTo, and Import.\n- Preserve jsonl as the default backend path so day-1 behavior does not change.\n\nNON-SCOPE\n- Backend selection config plumbing.\n- Package test matrix broadening.\n- WebSocket subscription smoke tests.","events":[{"actor":"ddx","body":"{\"resolved_provider\":\"codex\",\"resolved_model\":\"gpt-5.4-mini\",\"fallback_chain\":[],\"actual_power\":8}","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","kind":"routing","source":"ddx agent execute-bead","summary":"provider=codex model=gpt-5.4-mini"},{"actor":"ddx","body":"{\"attempt_id\":\"20260505T164659-abc25e07\",\"harness\":\"codex\",\"model\":\"gpt-5.4-mini\",\"input_tokens\":285426,\"output_tokens\":2755,\"total_tokens\":288181,\"cost_usd\":0,\"duration_ms\":34343,\"exit_code\":0}","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","kind":"cost","source":"ddx agent execute-bead","summary":"tokens=288181 model=gpt-5.4-mini"},{"actor":"erik","body":"The bead is too large for this execution depth and cannot be cleanly split further here. Completing it would require coordinated changes across cli/internal/bead/axon_backend.go, cli/internal/bead/axon/*, store/backend plumbing, and the axon-backed test matrix, while the bead is already at the depth cap. The requested real Axon GraphQL path is also still blocked on the upstream dependencies noted in the bead metadata (axon-05c1019d and axon-82b6f7b2), so I am not making speculative partial changes.","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","kind":"no_changes_needs_investigation","source":"ddx agent work","summary":"no_changes_needs_investigation"},{"actor":"erik","body":"no_changes\nrationale: status: needs_investigation\nreason: The bead is too large for this execution depth and cannot be cleanly split further here. Completing it would require coordinated changes across cli/internal/bead/axon_backend.go, cli/internal/bead/axon/*, store/backend plumbing, and the axon-backed 